title: #92Noon LaVelle in for PA! Topkin/Falvey/Russo/Garver
description: LaVelle E. Neal III fills in for PA today and welcomes a treasure trove of guests including the Tampa Bay Times' Marc Topkin, Twins' Executive Vice President and Chief Baseball Officer Derek Falvey, The Athletic's Michael Russo and Twins catcher Mitch Garver!
